1
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:10,260
=Dungeon Archive=

2
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:11,840
The killers of the case are...

3
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:13,320
Ning Waver

4
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:14,760
and Ke Stubborn.

5
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:15,800
Nice!

6
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:19,920
We never lost, Ning.

7
00:00:20,140 --> 00:00:21,540
(Killers escaped)

8
00:00:21,540 --> 00:00:23,460
(Ning Waver. Ke Stubborn)

9
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:25,340
(Case reconstruction)

10
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:27,240
We are the killers of the case.

11
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:28,280
Ning Waver.

12
00:00:28,280 --> 00:00:29,120
Ke Stubborn.

13
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:30,960
To save the children of Tui City,

14
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,430
stop the evil from doing bad,

15
00:00:32,430 --> 00:00:33,800
(Tomb of leader of Shi Damen Sect)
and to avenge our mentor.

16
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:34,920
We worked together

17
00:00:34,920 --> 00:00:36,280
to kill Lord Tui.

18
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:37,200
Six months ago,

19
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:38,760
(Four Symbols Manual)
I obtained a martial arts manual.

20
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:40,040
(There are four top secret skills)
After six months of studying it,

21
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:41,400
I finally learned all four moves.

22
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:44,000
(Countering move: Cosmic Absorbing Skill)
So I started planning my kill.

23
00:00:45,160 --> 00:00:47,400
(21 May, Year 260 of Tui)
On 21 May, my inner power recovered.

24
00:00:47,400 --> 00:00:49,200
(Tomb of leader of Shi Damen Sect)
It was time to avenge my mentor.

25
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:51,520
I am no match for Lord Tui
in a head-on confrontation.

26
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:53,080
So I tried to find his weakness

27
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,560
from Ning Waver.

28
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:55,700
(22 May, Year 260 of Tui)
On 22 May,

29
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:57,600
(Chivalry Manor)
I sneaked into Chivalry Manor.

30
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:59,520
I saw Ning Waver holding

31
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:01,040
the Eleven-Spice Tendon Powder.

32
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:04,200
Ning actually betrayed mentor.

33
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,310
I wanted to kill him.

34
00:01:05,310 --> 00:01:06,880
(23 May, Year 260 of Tui)
On 23 May,

35
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:07,920
I already have the perfect plan

36
00:01:07,920 --> 00:01:10,080
to kill Lord Tui in my mind,

37
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,680
but I need a helper.

38
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,960
But after taking him as my father,

39
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,880
I have no one anymore.

40
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,560
I wondered where

41
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:20,520
I can find someone
who can help me wholeheartedly.

42
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:22,720
(24 May, Year 260 of Tui)
On 24 May,

43
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:24,600
I sneaked into Ning Waver's room
once again

44
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:27,840
(Special tonic to recover inner power)
and found a familiar potion.

45
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:30,240
It looked exactly like the potion
that saved me.

46
00:01:30,240 --> 00:01:31,760
(Cures only Eleven-Spice Tendon Powder)
So the antidote was from him.

47
00:01:32,480 --> 00:01:33,780
(Special tonic to recover inner power)
I was stunned.

48
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,440
If he really had killed mentor,

49
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:36,040
(Tomb of leader of Shi Damen Sect)

50
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,800
why did he save me?

51
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,440
After all, I wanted
to take revenge against him.

52
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:42,040
The door opened at this time.

53
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,920
Ning Waver stood at the door.

54
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,280
Unbothered, he said,

55
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:46,960
"I am here."

56
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,720
(24 May, Year 260 of Tui)
On 24 May, I returned to my room

57
00:01:49,720 --> 00:01:51,360
to see my junior, Ke Stubborn,

58
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:54,000
standing inside.

59
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,880
He found the antidote in my room.

60
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,960
I hid it for so long,

61
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,400
and he finally found it.

62
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,120
He asked if I gave him the antidote.

63
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:02,640
I kept silent.

64
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,200
He questioned why I didn't tell him.

65
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,360
I didn't answer.

66
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,080
He asked me how I spent
the past two years.

67
00:02:08,910 --> 00:02:09,960
I still didn't answer him.

68
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:13,240
Some words can't be spoken.

69
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,400
But since he has found out,

70
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,720
it's pointless to pretend

71
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,240
to be the bad guy and kick him out.

72
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,320
After some thought,

73
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:23,840
I decided to ask him to help me.

74
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,560
I told him

75
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:28,360
(Meeting hall)
I'd fight Lord Tui in the meeting hall.

76
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:32,080
(Meow)
I'll make him use his strongest moves.

77
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:35,320
Then we'll both freeze
in front of the door.

78
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:37,320
Ke needs to take that opportunity

79
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:40,440
to piece my chest
with the Qide Sword from outside

80
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:44,520
and stab it into Lord Tui's heart.

81
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,520
After hearing the plan,

82
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,880
I refused him.

83
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:49,520
Why does he get
to be the hero every time?

84
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,280
If we go down, we go down together.

85
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,960
I don't need Ning
to stand in front of me.

86
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,400
But Ning said I'll need

87
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:58,440
(Four Symbols Manual)
a long time to learn those four moves.

88
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:00,840
But he had been poisoned.

89
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,000
He can't wait that long.

90
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:05,080
If I refused him today,

91
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,040
before long,

92
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,800
he would die for nothing.

93
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,280
Everything he did for the past two years
would be wasted.

94
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,320
He asked me to grant his wish.

95
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:15,160
He even planned my escape.

96
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:17,400
He wanted me to keep living.

97
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,160
I looked at him hand on my shoulder.

98
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,160
Five years ago,

99
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,840
they pulled me from the cliff.

100
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,000
Five years later,

101
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,440
it was leading me
into a mission with no return.

102
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,680
Ning,

103
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:31,360
if your path leads
to a sea of suffering,

104
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,200
I shall see it through.

105
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,240
I listened to his plan.

106
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,760
Before midnight strikes tomorrow night,

107
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:40,210
- Ke has to dress in black
- Young master is fighting someone!

108
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,280
and appear before Tui's subordinate

109
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:41,920
Catch up!

110
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:42,440
with his face covered.

111
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:44,680
He has to pretend to hunt me down
with the Qide Sword.

112
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,920
We will pass a corner.

113
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:51,320
Ke will change into the clothes
he'd hidden there

114
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,600
and pass me the sword.

115
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:55,000
He will then head to the inn

116
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,640
and use the innkeeper as an alibi

117
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,480
to prove he wasn't the Black-Robed Man.

118
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:02,560
At the same time,
we'd put a dummy there.

119
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,040
I'll dress it in my coat.

120
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:08,000
My inner clothes
matched Ke's black outfit.

121
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,080
I put on the mask

122
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,720
and pretend to be Ke with the sword.

123
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,680
He's carrying Young Lord Tui away!

124
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,160
Quick. Young master is in danger!

125
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,840
I'd carry the dummy disguised as me

126
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:18,720
along Lord Tui's usual route

127
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,570
(Meeting hall)
before entering the meeting hall.

128
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,480
Qide Sword will lure Lord Tui over.

129
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,840
Qide Sword?

130
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,720
- My lightness skill is the best.
- Don't you hare harm my son!

131
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:29,200
I can hide the sword in the yard

132
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,640
before he catches up to me

133
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:34,000
and put my coat on the dummy back on.

134
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:37,080
Once Lord Tui entered the meeting hall,

135
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,560
I'll lock it from inside

136
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:42,120
(Meeting hall)
and fight him according to our plan.

137
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:45,660
(Truth Inn)

138
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,880
After getting my alibi
from the innkeeper,

139
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,280
I'll leave the inn

140
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,440
and take off my coat
before going to the meeting hall.

141
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,320
(Chivalry Manor)
I'll wait for Ning

142
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:55,280
to make Lord Tui use his four moves.

143
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,760
When they are stuck at the door,

144
00:04:57,520 --> 00:04:59,560
I'll thrust the paper-thin Qide Sword

145
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,680
through the crack in the door,

146
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,640
piercing Ning's right chest

147
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,880
before driving it into Lord Tui's heart,

148
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,720
killing him

149
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,480
and Ning together.

150
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:11,080
(26 May, Year 260 of Tui. 10:55PM)
26 May, 10:55PM

151
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:13,080
I dressed in black with a face cover

152
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:14,280
to become the Black-Robed Man.

153
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,480
(26 May, Year 260 of Tui. 10:56PM)
At 10:56PM,

154
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,720
Ke pursued me with the Qide Sword.

155
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,320
Tui's subordinate
came after us as expected.

156
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:22,240
We quickly went around
to the back of the building

157
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,280
and got changed as planned.

158
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:27,760
I got on the main street
while wearing my coat.

159
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:29,000
(Truth Inn)
At 10:59PM,

160
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,200
(10:59PM)
I entered the inn to get a drink

161
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,240
(Houdan chicken. Pork noodles)
and met Yang and Ding.

162
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:34,320
The night watchman announced the time.

163
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,600
(11:02PM)
It was two minutes pass 11.

164
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,160
(Truth Inn)
I left the inn.

165
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,600
My plan was carried out perfectly.

166
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,080
Lord Tui entered as expected.

167
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:41,920
(Chivalry Manor)

168
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,320
I locked the door and fought him.

169
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,360
When the last move was used,

170
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,960
we were stuck at the door.

171
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,520
Lord Tui widened his eyes.

172
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:52,160
Disbelief and fear filled his eyes.

173
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:52,680
I know.

174
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,160
The moment I've been waiting
for two years

175
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,640
is finally here.

176
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,120
(11:05PM)
Five minutes pass 11.

177
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:01,200
I thrust Qide Sword
through the door crack.

178
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,120
It pierced Ning Waver's chest

179
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,680
and went straight into Lord Tui's heart.

180
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:07,920
Mentor, we finally avenged you.

181
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,360
I put on the coat again

182
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,240
and burned the black shirt
and face mask.

183
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,320
I then buried Qide Sword

184
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:14,200
back into mentor's grave
as per Ning's orders.

185
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,440
(Tomb of leader of Shi Damen Sect)
After doing that,

186
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,600
I looked up at the moon

187
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,280
and recalled what Ning once said.

188
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:20,360
- Mentor. Ning.
- Mentor. Ke.

189
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,200
We walked different paths
but share the same goal.

190
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:25,160
We shall meet the same end.

191
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:27,560
And I will eventually find my path.

192
00:06:28,340 --> 00:06:30,580
(Liu Yuning player log archive)

193
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:31,220
(Identity update. Ning Waver)

194
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:32,020
(Young master of Chivalry Manor)

195
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:32,860
(Awakened with all memories gone)

196
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,600
I am player, Liu Yuning.

197
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,480
In this case,

198
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:39,080
I play Chivalry Manor's
young master, Ning Waver.

199
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,320
This is my first time

200
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:41,960
playing a character with amnesia.

201
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:43,720
All I remember is waking up last night

202
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,920
and being told

203
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,080
that my godfather is dead.

204
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:49,280
I came to the Blade Gala
to find the suspect.

205
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:52,080
I didn't expect

206
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:53,240
- that He Ha
- Who?

207
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:55,400
would acknowledge me as the detective

208
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:57,200
and said I had died last night.

209
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,400
That was absurd.

210
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:02,160
I was standing right there.

211
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,720
And I wasn't wounded
per his claims.

212
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:07,020
(Doubtful until there's solid proof)
Something was off.

213
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,520
After examining the body,

214
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,520
I confirmed Lord Tui

215
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,560
was killed by Qide Sword.

216
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,840
(Wound confirms cause of death)
He was killed by the Qide Sword.

217
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,200
And that was the fatal blow.

218
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:18,680
But isn't the Qide Sword inside the inn?

219
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:23,040
I can't believe everyone was scolding me

220
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,760
during the investigation.

221
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,280
- Jin called me a lapdog.
- Lapdog!

222
00:07:26,770 --> 00:07:28,360
- I wanted to kick her out.
- Ning the Lapdog.

223
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,760
Are they taking advantage of my amnesia,

224
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,700
thinking I won't remember?

225
00:07:30,700 --> 00:07:32,660
(Doubtful)
What?

226
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,560
Or was I really

227
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,440
that kind of bully in the past?

228
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:36,880
(Reassessing his identity from testimonies)
You better leave.

229
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:40,200
Then Ding said
I killed his mentor, Uncle Meng.

230
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:43,480
But he's never seen
what Uncle Meng looked like.

231
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,000
So I started to guess

232
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,040
who I really was.

233
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,300
(Forming new theory
about his identity through testimonies)

234
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,600
Even though I may look like the bad guy

235
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,600
to everyone else now,

236
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,640
the truth could very well
be the total opposite.

237
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,640
Later on,

238
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,000
I found out

239
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,000
I was once the lead disciple

240
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:03,080
of Shi Damen Sect from Ke's story.

241
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:03,940
(Piecing together his identity
through others' testimony)

242
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:07,000
I only took the enemy as my father
after my master died.

243
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,840
At Chivalry Manor, you took the enemy
as your father.

244
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,760
That clue made me even more sure.

245
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:13,080
I guessed I must've had a reason.

246
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:15,260
(Suspecting a hidden motive)
That's why I stayed close to Lord Tui.

247
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,520
Since the mysterious man
with the Qide Sword

248
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,120
had been to Ghost Market,

249
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,560
we followed his trail there too.

250
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,440
At Master Gui's place,

251
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:24,360
(Four Ultimate Skills: Hedong Roar)
we got the man's martial arts manual.

252
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,200
We also learned he
didn't have long to live.

253
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,800
Based on that manual

254
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:30,120
and the fight marks in the meeting hall,

255
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:32,260
we reconstructed how the victim
and someone else

256
00:08:32,260 --> 00:08:33,400
(Based on the known moves)
fought inside the room.

257
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:35,440
(Figuring out the victim's route)
Each of them made four moves.

258
00:08:35,789 --> 00:08:37,000
We realized that in the end,

259
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,000
the two of them would be frozen
face-to-face by the door.

260
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,150
(Meeting hall floor plan)
Through deduction,

261
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:43,280
we learned this was a locked room.

262
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,200
Then how did the killer
leave the crime scene?

263
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:50,640
Or maybe the killer never went in.

264
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,720
Kill without entering?

265
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,120
They killed from outside
the door with a sword.

266
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,640
So he had to kill Ning.

267
00:08:57,640 --> 00:09:00,440
We found marks on the door crack.

268
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:00,960
Run over.

269
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,720
(Based on the marks on the door crack)
No need to open the door.

270
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,560
(Inferring the accomplice's route)
No need to go in.

271
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:05,040
Kill him here, pull out the sword,
and leave.

272
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,520
Then the person inside the room

273
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:08,860
fighting Lord Tui could only be me.

274
00:09:08,860 --> 00:09:10,080
(Tracing the accomplice's actions
confirms his part in the murder)

275
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,820
(Putting the clues together)
So I'm one of the killers.

276
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,440
- When, in the meeting hall courtyard,
- This is it.

277
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,880
we found the black inner robe,

278
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:17,760
I realized

279
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,500
my partner in crime

280
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:21,100
(Identifying his teammate)
was Ke Stubborn.

281
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:23,840
Because before we left for Ghost Market,

282
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:26,080
Ke secretly pulled at my outer robe.

283
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,960
He checked the color of my inner robe.

284
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,920
Then he said,

285
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:30,880
"Good thing you took it off".

286
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,520
I didn't get it back then.

287
00:09:32,520 --> 00:09:34,220
(Confirming his teammate)
Now I understand.

288
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,600
He was checking

289
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:37,200
whether I'd taken off the inner robe.

290
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,600
He was worried I'd expose myself.

291
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,320
(Confirmed partner and strategy)
Once I knew who my partner was,

292
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,200
I had a direction.

293
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,040
In the final discussion,

294
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:46,080
starting from emotional motive,

295
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:48,520
everyone thought my helper

296
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:51,680
was probably someone more likely
to realize I was a good person

297
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:53,080
and someone close to me.

298
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:55,200
They thought Ding and Ke
were more suspicious.

299
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:56,720
One of them was your master.

300
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,280
(Adding wrong votes to escape)
So I played along.

301
00:09:58,510 --> 00:09:59,000
Let's suspect him.

302
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,680
I voted for myself and Ding.

303
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,400
(Voting window)
To add more wrong votes.

304
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:06,220
(Zhou Keyu player log archive)

305
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:06,900
(Identity info: Ke Stubborn)

306
00:10:06,900 --> 00:10:07,740
(Junior disciple of a Prestigious Sect)

307
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:08,500
(The boat has moved,
but the sword hasn't)

308
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,240
I'm player Zhou Keyu.

309
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,200
In this case,

310
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:14,960
I play Ke Stubborn, the junior disciple
of a Prestigious Sect.

311
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,560
I'm also one of the killers
in this case.

312
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:19,160
I came to Truth Inn for the Blade Gala.

313
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:21,080
I didn't expect someone
to push the door open.

314
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,240
And that person was Ning Waver.

315
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:24,920
How is that possible?

316
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:27,040
Last night, I ran him through.

317
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,160
There's no way he survived.

318
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,200
At the Blade Gala,

319
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,760
Ning Waver said he'd lost his memory.

320
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,660
I lost my memory.

321
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:36,560
He only remembered that he was
the young master of Chivalry Manor.

322
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,320
What on earth is going on?

323
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,080
(A dead accomplice returns)
Is he still my senior brother?

324
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,780
(Lying low and watching in secret)

325
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,640
As the investigation went deeper,

326
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,720
- I thought only I wanted Ning Waver
- You traitor!

327
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,040
and Lord Tui dead.

328
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:49,520
But I didn't expect Jin...

329
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:50,600
Lapdog!

330
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:50,920
Ding...

331
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,240
You killed him.

332
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,040
And Yang

333
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,520
(Analyzing others' clues)
all had motives too.

334
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,720
So I just needed to muddy the waters.

335
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:58,340
(Muddied the waters)
Then I could get away clean.

336
00:10:58,540 --> 00:10:59,500
Before we went to Ghost Market,

337
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:00,500
I waited until no one was around

338
00:11:00,500 --> 00:11:01,820
and got close to Ning Waver.

339
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:03,660
I didn't know if he was faking amnesia

340
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:05,060
or if he really had amnesia.

341
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:06,740
(Hinting at his accomplice role)
So I whispered,

342
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:07,980
"Good thing you took it off".

343
00:11:09,140 --> 00:11:10,500
I hoped he would remember

344
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:12,260
everything that happened yesterday.

345
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:14,220
While sorting out the timeline,

346
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:15,620
I brought up a new idea.

347
00:11:16,100 --> 00:11:17,900
If the killer committed the crime,

348
00:11:17,900 --> 00:11:18,620
they must've known

349
00:11:18,620 --> 00:11:21,180
that a fierce fight was happening
at Chivalry Manor.

350
00:11:21,180 --> 00:11:22,180
(Deliberately misleading
an important point)

351
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,420
(Avoiding suspicion)
The killer had to time it

352
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:25,460
with the ten-breath freeze.

353
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:27,540
They had to hit the moment
when both of them were frozen.

354
00:11:27,540 --> 00:11:30,780
Then I was the first one
to enter Truth Inn.

355
00:11:30,780 --> 00:11:31,780
When I went to buy wine...

356
00:11:31,780 --> 00:11:33,940
Ding and Yang left
the inn right on time.

357
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:35,860
(Shifts suspicion onto others)

358
00:11:35,860 --> 00:11:38,340
They both had obvious
muscle-memory movements.

359
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:40,020
So I guided everyone

360
00:11:40,020 --> 00:11:42,300
(Uses gap to suspect Yang and Ding)
to focus on that timeline.

361
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:44,180
The killer couldn't stay
at the inn for long.

362
00:11:44,180 --> 00:11:45,260
They had to go and come back fast.

363
00:11:46,900 --> 00:11:49,700
And the more exact the timing was,
the more suspicious they seemed.

364
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:51,220
Or rather, the closer they were

365
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:52,580
(Thinking from the killer's mindset)
to the exact hour of Zi,

366
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:54,180
(Makes nearby timing seem suspicious)
the more suspicious they are.

367
00:11:54,740 --> 00:11:56,940
So time-wise, I felt Yang

368
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,820
had a bigger chance of being the killer.

369
00:11:58,820 --> 00:12:00,420
Ding immediately agreed with me.

370
00:12:01,020 --> 00:12:02,620
(Voting window)
In the final voting round,

371
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:04,140
(Meeting hall)
I felt Ding looked like

372
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:05,500
someone who was in a rush
to leave the inn

373
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:06,980
to create an alibi.

374
00:12:06,980 --> 00:12:08,220
He wanted to fake an alibi.

375
00:12:08,220 --> 00:12:09,300
(Analyzing the situation)
One very important point...

376
00:12:09,300 --> 00:12:10,100
Motive-wise,

377
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,220
if it came down to me or Ding,

378
00:12:11,660 --> 00:12:13,060
Ding was my fall guy.

379
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:14,100
(Locks onto a fall guy
to increase wrong votes)

380
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:16,180
So in the end, I voted

381
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:18,260
for Ding Pillar and Ning Waver.

382
00:12:19,580 --> 00:12:21,860
(Jin Jing player log archive)

383
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:22,420
(Identity info: Jin Thrifty)

384
00:12:22,420 --> 00:12:23,060
(Owner of Truth Inn)

385
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:23,620
(A hidden sword waits
for its benefactor)

386
00:12:23,620 --> 00:12:25,300
I'm player Jin Jing.

387
00:12:25,300 --> 00:12:28,220
In this case, I play
the owner of Truth Inn,

388
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,260
Jin Thrifty.

389
00:12:29,430 --> 00:12:31,900
- Noon, May 27.
- The Blade Gala is about to begin.

390
00:12:31,900 --> 00:12:33,900
- The inn is hosting the Blade Gala.
- Everyone, follow me.

391
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:36,540
Just as we were about to start,

392
00:12:36,540 --> 00:12:38,860
someone named He Ha
brought a group of people in.

393
00:12:38,860 --> 00:12:41,260
They carried Lord Tui's body inside.

394
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:43,540
I was shocked.

395
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:45,580
That monster hiding behind a kind face

396
00:12:45,580 --> 00:12:46,620
was actually dead.

397
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:49,020
Besides me,

398
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:50,420
someone else hated him too.

399
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:53,460
When we searched Lord Tui's body,

400
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:56,660
we found what looked like sword wounds.

401
00:12:56,660 --> 00:12:58,700
There were no other clues.

402
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:00,780
At first,

403
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:03,220
(Links wounds to the weapon)
we thought he was killed with the sword.

404
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:06,580
And I was clearly the owner
of the Qide Sword.

405
00:13:06,980 --> 00:13:08,380
So the first thing they questioned

406
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:10,620
was where I got that sword from.

407
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:11,380
It's mine.

408
00:13:11,380 --> 00:13:12,740
To clear my name,

409
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:13,660
I told them everything.

410
00:13:13,660 --> 00:13:14,580
(Reveals where the Qide Sword came
from to lower suspicion)

411
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:15,460
At that moment,

412
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:18,140
Ning Waver suggested
that everyone present

413
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:19,300
try pulling out the sword.

414
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:20,860
Whoever can pull it out

415
00:13:20,860 --> 00:13:22,020
might be the killer.

416
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:24,260
After everyone failed to draw it,

417
00:13:24,260 --> 00:13:27,300
He Ha said he was the one who forged it.

418
00:13:27,300 --> 00:13:29,220
It was indeed a fake sword.

419
00:13:30,020 --> 00:13:31,100
The moment he said that,

420
00:13:31,100 --> 00:13:32,620
I was completely stunned.

421
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:35,740
Then everyone started searching my inn.

422
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:37,580
They also searched the martial arts
school across the street.

423
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:40,260
They found clues about Yang Glory,

424
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:41,700
Ding Pillar,

425
00:13:42,300 --> 00:13:44,140
and Ke Stubborn.

426
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,820
After hearing everyone's stories,

427
00:13:46,050 --> 00:13:46,570
I realized

428
00:13:46,590 --> 00:13:48,640
everyone hated Lord Tui

429
00:13:48,650 --> 00:13:49,620
and Ning Waver.

430
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:50,420
(Connects the clues and finds
that everyone had a motive)

431
00:13:50,540 --> 00:13:53,660
After that, we went
to the crime scene, Chivalry Manor.

432
00:13:53,660 --> 00:13:54,580
(Based on the crime scene investigation)
At first glance,

433
00:13:54,580 --> 00:13:56,740
(Suspects it was a locked-room murder)
it looked like a locked-room murder.

434
00:13:56,740 --> 00:13:58,420
A locked-room murder.

435
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:01,340
(Finds a clue)
I found bamboo slips on the floor.

436
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:02,700
They were all over the place.

437
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:05,020
I knew that definitely wasn't normal.

438
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:07,220
(Links odd items to a mechanism)
Maybe they were part of some mechanism.

439
00:14:07,260 --> 00:14:08,580
Just then,

440
00:14:08,580 --> 00:14:11,660
a strange sound suddenly came
from the inner room of the meeting hall.

441
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:13,660
Everyone went in to check it out.

442
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:14,540
There,

443
00:14:14,540 --> 00:14:17,260
we got a lot of clues about Lord Tui.

444
00:14:18,580 --> 00:14:20,780
After reading the details inside,

445
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:23,340
I suddenly felt Ning Waver was strange.

446
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:26,100
He used to be Master Meng's
eldest disciple.

447
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:29,170
But after Master Meng died,

448
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:30,620
he accepted

449
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:31,820
Lord Tui as his godfather so quickly.

450
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:34,140
Was he really a bad guy,

451
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:36,140
or was he only pretending to submit?

452
00:14:36,140 --> 00:14:37,900
(Suspects Ning had a hidden reason)
I suddenly wasn't so sure.

453
00:14:38,060 --> 00:14:39,020
At Master Gui's place,

454
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:40,740
we got some very important information

455
00:14:40,740 --> 00:14:43,260
left behind by a mysterious person.

456
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:44,860
This mysterious person

457
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:47,740
helped me pay off the money
I borrowed from the bank.

458
00:14:47,740 --> 00:14:49,380
Who exactly was this mysterious person?

459
00:14:50,980 --> 00:14:53,580
With the clues we got from Master Gui,

460
00:14:53,580 --> 00:14:55,100
we returned to the meeting hall.

461
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:56,860
Based on the four moves,

462
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:58,890
(Traces the moves before death)
we worked out the attack order.

463
00:14:58,890 --> 00:14:59,900
It went up to here.

464
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:01,460
While everyone was discussing,

465
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:03,180
I suddenly had a flash of inspiration.

466
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:04,940
I had a bold theory.

467
00:15:04,940 --> 00:15:06,180
I guessed this was all a setup.

468
00:15:06,180 --> 00:15:07,220
(Reviews the clues and boldly predicts
there was a premeditated setup)

469
00:15:07,220 --> 00:15:08,020
Ning Waver

470
00:15:08,020 --> 00:15:10,420
must've been wearing a black cloak then.

471
00:15:10,420 --> 00:15:12,660
He carried something else
to throw everyone off.

472
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:14,340
And the dummy was faked
with the cuju ball.

473
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:17,780
Ning Waver must've been very close
to Master Gui.

474
00:15:18,180 --> 00:15:19,820
He left those things with him.

475
00:15:20,540 --> 00:15:22,140
He quietly did a lot of good things.

476
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:23,300
(Tonic that restores inner strength)
He soon got his inner strength back.

477
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:24,060
(Based on the fight scene)
I think

478
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:26,700
(Guessing inside help)
the killer planned it with Ning Waver.

479
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:28,140
We agreed to kill Lord Tui together.

480
00:15:28,140 --> 00:15:29,740
Ning Waver must be a good guy.

481
00:15:30,900 --> 00:15:33,500
The killer had no choice
but to kill Ning then.

482
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:34,180
They had to kill you too.

483
00:15:34,540 --> 00:15:36,220
(A bold guess based on the scene)
Maybe there's more to it.

484
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,140
(The killer didn't plan to kill Ning)
I realized you were a good guy.

485
00:15:37,140 --> 00:15:39,580
(Guessing there's more behind this)
The killer didn't mean to kill Ning.

486
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:42,180
In the end, we found marks on the door.

487
00:15:42,820 --> 00:15:44,780
We worked out how the killer did it.

488
00:15:44,780 --> 00:15:46,460
(Using the marks at the scene)
That also proved my theory.

489
00:15:46,460 --> 00:15:47,260
(Confirmed that Ning willingly
joined the plan)

490
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:48,580
During the trial,

491
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:50,900
we each shared our own timeline.

492
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,780
I knew I didn't kill anyone.

493
00:15:53,060 --> 00:15:54,180
So the killer had to be

494
00:15:54,180 --> 00:15:54,700
Ke,

495
00:15:54,700 --> 00:15:55,020
Ding,

496
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:56,300
Yang,

497
00:15:57,260 --> 00:15:58,460
or Ning.

498
00:15:58,460 --> 00:16:00,100
Starting with the motive,

499
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:02,980
I thought Ding and Ke were more likely
to find out Ning was good.

500
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:04,420
Then one of them became the accomplice.

501
00:16:04,420 --> 00:16:04,900
After I came out,

502
00:16:04,900 --> 00:16:06,780
you rushed over and bumped into me.

503
00:16:06,780 --> 00:16:09,540
Because Yang said Ding
hurriedly bumped into her,

504
00:16:09,540 --> 00:16:10,900
I found that really suspicious.

505
00:16:10,900 --> 00:16:12,300
(Using witness details
to narrow down the suspect)

506
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:13,340
The killer wanted to make

507
00:16:13,340 --> 00:16:15,180
(Maybe staged contact)
the contact memorable

508
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:16,940
(To strengthen the alibi)
to strengthen their alibi.

509
00:16:17,660 --> 00:16:18,180
So

510
00:16:18,180 --> 00:16:21,460
I finally voted for Ding Pillar
and Ning Waver.

511
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,500
(Voting window)

512
00:16:22,540 --> 00:16:24,820
(TNT, Ding Chengxin player log archive)

513
00:16:24,860 --> 00:16:25,500
