515
00:16:26,340 --> 00:16:27,100
(Hidden talents, searching
for the chivalrous path)

516
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:28,860
I'm player Ding Chengxin.

517
00:16:28,860 --> 00:16:29,820
In this case,

518
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:32,180
I play the young waiter at Truth Inn,

